{
	Description = {
		"@eng:Homing : when outside \'WorldRadius\', particles are pushed back inwards.\\nWrap : when particles touch the world boundaries, they teleport to the opposite side.\\nWrapBox : like \'Wrap\', but the world is considered a cube, not a sphere. Can produce more stable wrapping behavior.\\nBounce : particles bounce on the world boundaries.",
	};
